  "text": "The proposed network is trained on NVIDIA GeForce GTX 1080 Ti GPU and tested on Mac Pro with 2.7 GHz Intel Core i5 CPU. Similar to [CITATION_1] , the input training pair is randomly croped as size of 256 × 256 after downsampled by a factor of two. Weights are initialized to follow Gaussian distribution with zeros mean and standard deviation 0.02. For each iteration of optimization, 1 step is performed on discriminator D, followed by 2 steps on generator G to prevent discriminator loss L d from zero. The model is trained for 15 epochs within 2 days, comparing with 200 epochs for 6 days in [CITATION_2] . Furthermore, despite of instability GAN's training, our method converges to similar result for each and every training task, which demonstrates the robustness of our GAN architecture. ",
